            "currentCldrName": "Memo",
            "description": "<p>A white piece of paper with text written on it by a yellow <a href=\"/pencil/\">pencil</a>, positioned over the sheet, tip down, at a 45&deg; angle. Commonly used for content concerning various types of documents and writing, including signing (in sports).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WhatsApp and Facebook&rsquo;s designs depict an old-fashioned office <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memorandum\">memorandum</a> on pink paper. Apple&rsquo;s suggests an informal note with the easter egg of handwritten text from its 1997&ndash;2002 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Think_different\"><i>Crazy Ones/Think Different</i></a> ad campaign: <em>Here&rsquo;s to the crazy ones. The misfits. The rebels. The troublemakers. The round pegs in the square holes</em>&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not to be confused with <a href=\"/page-facing-up/\">üìÑ Page Facing Up</a> or other emojis featuring sheets of paper.</p>",
